@AI_Generated_Chat_System.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5022
@token = your_jwt_token_here
@username = testuser

### Assign Role to User
# Available roles: "Super Admin", "Admin", "Teacher", "Student", "Finance Officer"
POST {{AI_Generated_Chat_System.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/{{username}}/assign-role
Content-Type: application/json

"Admin"

### Test Admin-Only Endpoint
GET {{AI_Generated_Chat_System.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Finance-Only Endpoint
GET {{AI_Generated_Chat_System.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/finance-only
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
